{"tid":1374754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪慣左無委任證？叫都唔攞？係咪慣左過份使用武力？記者影住照打？","createTime":"2019-07-28T00:48:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T00:53:22.000Z","uid":74778,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b6545de5a71c3b4591d1948693964bb3d84040e5","tid":1374754,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T00:48:05.000Z","msg":"每次示威都有喺巿民要求下唔出示委任證而自稱警員嘅人士執法 使用武力驅趕市民<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190708/_2019070823245895947.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190708%2F_2019070823245895947.jpg&h=8643c295&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1039778/即時-香港-逃犯條例-警務處-便衣人員行使警察權力需表明身分及出示委任證\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1039778%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E8%AD%A6%E5%8B%99%E8%99%95-%E4%BE%BF%E8%A1%A3%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E8%A1%8C%E4%BD%BF%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E6%AC%8A%E5%8A%9B%E9%9C%80%E8%A1%A8%E6%98%8E%E8%BA%AB%E5%88%86%E5%8F%8A%E5%87%BA%E7%A4%BA%E5%A7%94%E4%BB%BB%E8%AD%89&d=ajJRCbjZ3CJF8zdY8%2Fu%2F11DHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=af46e96b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1039778%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E8%AD%A6%E5%8B%99%E8%99%95-%E4%BE%BF%E8%A1%A3%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E8%A1%8C%E4%BD%BF%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E6%AC%8A%E5%8A%9B%E9%9C%80%E8%A1%A8%E6%98%8E%E8%BA%AB%E5%88%86%E5%8F%8A%E5%87%BA%E7%A4%BA%E5%A7%94%E4%BB%BB%E8%AD%89&h=3eb2e58f\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1039778/即時-香港-逃犯條例-警務處-便衣人員行使警察權力需表明身分及出示委任證</a><br />\n<br />\n兜口兜面叫佢出示，都唔出示，然後照執法，又有大量武裝。<strong>係咪大陸士兵？</strong><br />\n<br />\n政府又係咪唔回應？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj